03:23:16.028 --> 03:23:19.546
Why do we call it in Arabic hur (free)

03:23:19.546 --> 03:23:21.342
that you freed it from

03:23:21.342 --> 03:23:24.530
When you free a slice of meat

03:23:24.530 --> 03:23:26.896
from the body of an animal

03:23:26.896 --> 03:23:30.208
to free it or to free the rip

03:23:30.208 --> 03:23:31.608
it means you have cut it

03:23:31.608 --> 03:23:34.799
Freeing (tahrir in Arabic) is about finding the limits of something

03:23:34.799 --> 03:23:37.300
and you take it and you say, This is it.

03:23:37.300 --> 03:23:40.904
It is like editing (also tahrir in Arabic) books. It's the same principle.

03:23:40.904 --> 03:23:47.466
Freedom is to be free from within.

03:23:47.466 --> 03:23:50.855
Without needing anything

03:23:50.855 --> 03:23:57.150
And when all your feelings and all your being depend on the fact 

03:23:57.150 --> 03:24:01.998
that you will not be perfect unless you buy a Mercedes car

03:24:01.998 --> 03:24:05.075
then you have became a slave to it.

03:24:05.075 --> 03:24:10.195
The first one, the 'freedom from' is an enslavement freedom.

03:24:10.195 --> 03:24:14.038
And the 'freedom to' is the pure freedom.

03:24:14.038 --> 03:24:17.543
No one will be able to break you.

03:24:17.543 --> 03:24:19.774
It might be the other way around

03:24:19.774 --> 03:24:21.753
The 'freedom from' is the pure freedom.

03:24:21.753 --> 03:24:24.205
Yes, the 'freedom from' is the pure freedom.

03:24:24.205 --> 03:24:29.490
I can be a perfect human being within me.

03:24:29.490 --> 03:24:30.666
Strong

03:24:30.666 --> 03:24:34.740
I have that strong inner citadel that we talked about.

03:24:34.740 --> 03:24:39.361
A powerful citadel inside me that suffices me

03:24:39.361 --> 03:24:46.283
without the need to live in a luxury house

03:24:46.283 --> 03:24:49.284
or to owe money until Judgment Day

03:24:49.284 --> 03:24:53.603
just to be able to buy a luxury car to show my neighbors and friends

03:24:53.603 --> 03:24:55.494
This is slavery

03:24:55.494 --> 03:24:58.857
And as many people have written,

03:24:58.857 --> 03:25:03.613
especially about debt and what is debt, etc.

03:25:03.613 --> 03:25:06.959
They said that today

03:25:06.959 --> 03:25:14.225
we are slaves to capitalism even if we think that we are free.

03:25:14.225 --> 03:25:17.615
I want to take on other concepts.

03:25:17.615 --> 03:25:21.046
Equality for instance.

03:25:21.046 --> 03:25:26.283
What was this concept like before modernity?

03:25:26.283 --> 03:25:28.430
Was it present?

03:25:28.430 --> 03:25:30.868
All of these concepts

03:25:30.868 --> 03:25:36.328
We have equality, injustice, and justice. These ideas are popular today.

03:25:36.328 --> 03:25:39.635
Did they have a presence before modernity?

03:25:39.635 --> 03:25:47.863
Every society has a way of creating the necessary conditions

03:25:47.863 --> 03:25:51.442
to continue in life.

03:25:51.442 --> 03:25:52.983
Sometimes they suffer from some crises.

03:25:52.983 --> 03:25:54.319
All societies.

03:25:54.319 --> 03:25:57.802
The have their ups and downs.

03:25:57.802 --> 03:26:02.910
In these frameworks

03:26:02.910 --> 03:26:10.380
society always has the means to enable

03:26:10.380 --> 03:26:15.779
this things to spin around this wheel.

03:26:15.779 --> 03:26:22.287
Equality is a way to solve some problems

03:26:22.287 --> 03:26:30.423
so that society can continue its normal life.

03:26:30.423 --> 03:26:34.209
We can't say

03:26:34.209 --> 03:26:36.523
that our circumstances

03:26:36.523 --> 03:26:39.232
because it requires some kind of equality

03:26:39.232 --> 03:26:42.055
it must exist in any other society

03:26:42.055 --> 03:26:45.126
and we ask, Did they have equality or not?

03:26:45.126 --> 03:26:47.662
This question in itself is problematic.

03:26:47.662 --> 03:26:51.751
But was this dilemma present?

03:26:51.751 --> 03:26:54.501
There weren't problems of that kind.

03:26:54.501 --> 03:26:58.211
Because Shari'a, before the 19th century,

03:26:58.211 --> 03:27:01.495
had organized life

03:27:01.495 --> 03:27:06.055
and because of its importance to society

03:27:06.055 --> 03:27:09.933
and its holiness

03:27:09.933 --> 03:27:16.625
society accepted the provisions of Sharia almost as a second nature to them.

03:27:16.625 --> 03:27:24.949
Equality was not important to them in the sense that we interpret it.

03:27:24.949 --> 03:27:27.260
What is the meaning of equality?

03:27:27.260 --> 03:27:30.422
Let's say between male and female.

03:27:30.422 --> 03:27:35.497
As in the male and female are equal and have equal rights.

03:27:35.497 --> 03:27:38.616
But what does this mean?

03:27:38.616 --> 03:27:43.036
It means the female can work.

03:27:43.036 --> 03:27:49.288
And since she works the children will be at home

03:27:49.288 --> 03:27:52.818
and another person will take care of them

03:27:52.818 --> 03:27:55.868
What are the problems facing the children?

03:27:55.868 --> 03:27:58.004
Where is the father?

03:27:58.004 --> 03:28:01.314
Is he present in the children's life or not?

03:28:01.314 --> 03:28:03.311
Because he also has equality.

03:28:03.311 --> 03:28:08.161
If the female can go anywhere, he can as well.

03:28:08.161 --> 03:28:10.367
Ho about the children? The family?

03:28:10.367 --> 03:28:12.651
etc.

03:28:12.651 --> 03:28:16.149
Why do I use this situation specifically?

03:28:16.149 --> 03:28:21.000
Because why the female has a right to work?

03:28:21.000 --> 03:28:26.574
Because we are a capitalist society that measures everything with money

03:28:26.574 --> 03:28:30.939
When the woman becomes equal to the man

03:28:30.939 --> 03:28:39.531
she must do exactly what he used to do to be equal.

03:28:39.531 --> 03:28:45.368
If the man makes $100,000

03:28:45.368 --> 03:28:51.138
the woman must make about same.

03:28:51.138 --> 03:28:54.964
It became a material equality.

03:28:54.964 --> 03:28:57.633
But are men and women the same thing?

03:28:57.633 --> 03:29:01.573
The woman gives birth to the children and the man doesn't.

03:29:01.573 --> 03:29:05.777
When the children come, it's their responsibility.

03:29:05.777 --> 03:29:07.945
She has a little more even.

03:29:07.945 --> 03:29:11.615
It's not that she is forced to do it.

03:29:11.615 --> 03:29:15.904
But it's how nature works, because man can't breastfeeds his children.

03:29:15.904 --> 03:29:20.676
I'd love to do it for her if I could, but I can't.

03:29:20.676 --> 03:29:23.946
The mother is the only person who can breastfeeds her children.

03:29:23.946 --> 03:29:27.234
These are nature laws we cannot ignore.

03:29:27.234 --> 03:29:32.056
It enters into the problematic situation of equality.

03:29:32.056 --> 03:29:37.021
In my opinion, the Western woman, and the woman in general

03:29:37.021 --> 03:29:41.755
the more they are liberated, the more they are enslaved.

03:29:41.755 --> 03:29:44.946
Let's take a simple example

03:29:44.946 --> 03:29:50.641
Women are freed to go to the market and to work and bring money.

03:29:50.641 --> 03:29:55.204
Just like her husband, and sometimes more.

03:29:55.204 --> 03:29:58.343
She comes back home to cook

03:29:58.343 --> 03:30:05.890
because her husband is relaxing in front of football match

03:30:05.890 --> 03:30:07.959
and maybe he drinks as well

03:30:07.959 --> 03:30:10.543
While she worked all day

03:30:10.543 --> 03:30:14.333
and comes home to more work, surrounded by her kids yelling "mom, mom"

03:30:14.333 --> 03:30:16.970
few kids call their dad

03:30:16.970 --> 03:30:21.052
there are examples but not most

03:30:21.052 --> 03:30:24.628
She cooks and she does more

03:30:24.628 --> 03:30:30.986
Few men today who are equal to their wives in house work.

03:30:30.986 --> 03:30:33.716
Who is paying the bigger price?

03:30:33.716 --> 03:30:35.458
The woman.

03:30:35.458 --> 03:30:38.486
I don't mean that women shouldn't work.

03:30:38.486 --> 03:30:42.769
But you have many other considerations on the issue of equality.

03:30:42.769 --> 03:30:45.708
Muslims have figured it out.

03:30:45.708 --> 03:30:47.974
Everyone is assigned to a role.

03:30:47.974 --> 03:30:50.197
As al-Mawardi said,

03:30:50.197 --> 03:30:55.240
Every gathering is a collaboration.

03:30:55.240 --> 03:30:57.900
And everyone has his own importance.

03:30:57.900 --> 03:31:00.001
If you are housewife

03:31:00.001 --> 03:31:03.483
and someone says this is demeaning

03:31:03.483 --> 03:31:06.863
compared to who bring half a million dollar to the house

03:31:06.863 --> 03:31:11.305
this person is either blind to the truth

03:31:11.305 --> 03:31:14.500
or very stupid.

03:31:14.500 --> 03:31:16.864
Motherhood, in my opinion,

03:31:16.864 --> 03:31:23.073
and of course woman must be educated

03:31:23.073 --> 03:31:27.129
but when she is faced with motherhood,

03:31:27.129 --> 03:31:28.900
in a period of her life

03:31:28.900 --> 03:31:35.887
In my opinion, she should be appreciated more than a man who brings a million dollar home.

03:31:35.887 --> 03:31:38.420
However, this doesn't exist.

03:31:38.420 --> 03:31:42.151
Because when a mother have babies

03:31:42.151 --> 03:31:45.042
she doesn't benefit capitalism.

03:31:45.042 --> 03:31:48.022
Capitalism do not reward her.

03:31:48.022 --> 03:31:52.700
Few companies that give good rights

03:31:52.700 --> 03:31:56.065
Things are gradually improving now, as it should.

03:31:56.065 --> 03:31:58.924
I don't deny that.

03:31:58.924 --> 03:32:03.710
But for more than a hundred years

03:32:03.710 --> 03:32:08.846
women were enslaved because they wanted them to work and have children too

03:32:08.846 --> 03:32:10.388
without any..

03:32:10.388 --> 03:32:16.667
A woman must be at home, and she must be paid a very high salary

03:32:16.667 --> 03:32:20.496
because she is a mother.

03:32:20.496 --> 03:32:23.523
Does this happen in capitalism?

03:32:23.523 --> 03:32:25.324
No.

03:32:25.324 --> 03:32:28.028
The law of capitalism is money.

03:32:28.028 --> 03:32:30.001
There is no interest in

03:32:30.001 --> 03:32:38.309
Everything else is respected in the end, because it brings more money.

03:32:38.309 --> 03:32:43.882
If company gives donations to a museum or a charitable foundation

03:32:43.882 --> 03:32:46.935
because it reduce taxes and they put their name

03:32:46.935 --> 03:32:49.339
Rockefeller gives a lot of money, but why?

03:32:49.339 --> 03:32:54.613
Because of the moral and spiritual conviction and the theological?

03:32:54.613 --> 03:32:55.759
No.

03:32:55.759 --> 03:32:59.555
It gives him a big name

03:32:59.555 --> 03:33:02.456
people idolize him and love him more

03:33:02.456 --> 03:33:04.790
and this brings in more money.

03:33:04.790 --> 03:33:07.377
It's all about money.

03:33:07.377 --> 03:33:11.276
Equality is fundamentally a matter of materialism.

03:33:11.276 --> 03:33:16.713
There is not always a high regard for either men or women.

03:33:16.713 --> 03:33:21.126
The modernist human being is a disgraced one.

03:33:21.126 --> 03:33:25.555
Not to mention that he is empty within.

03:33:25.555 --> 03:33:34.000
The modernist state in your thesis the Impossible State,

03:33:34.000 --> 03:33:39.515
in summary, you say that any definition of a modern Islamic state

03:33:39.515 --> 03:33:43.095
is intrinsically self-contradictory

03:33:43.095 --> 03:33:45.035
And logically of course.

03:33:45.035 --> 03:33:47.650
Excuse me, but

03:33:47.650 --> 03:33:53.197
all the states are modern state

03:33:53.197 --> 03:33:58.040
We live in a modern state, I pray, fast and pay zakat.

03:33:58.040 --> 03:34:02.921
I practice all my Islamic practices.

03:34:02.921 --> 03:34:05.665
Where is the contradiction?

03:34:05.665 --> 03:34:08.600
I'd love for you to explain it more to me.

03:34:08.600 --> 03:34:13.749
Modern state

03:34:13.749 --> 03:34:21.794
It was established on the basis of separating morality from anything else.

03:34:21.794 --> 03:34:29.836
I could stop here, and ask you to analyze this statement.

03:34:29.836 --> 03:34:32.420
Correct, large and deep analysis.

03:34:32.420 --> 03:34:34.864
And you'll find all the answers there.

03:34:34.864 --> 03:34:37.548
Rather than getting into a long and wide maze.

03:34:37.548 --> 03:34:39.636
Just from this statement.

03:34:39.636 --> 03:34:47.315
The modern state is not interested in establishing

03:34:47.315 --> 03:34:49.955
a moral self.

03:34:49.955 --> 03:34:53.405
The moral self is the mayor of a responsible society.

03:34:53.405 --> 03:34:58.107
You cannot produce a responsible society without a moral self.

03:34:58.107 --> 03:35:03.531
Let me give you a small but important example.

03:35:03.531 --> 03:35:08.161
We'll take it from the end, as we say in Palestine.

03:35:08.161 --> 03:35:12.768
- Do you use this phrase in Saudi Arabia?
- Yes, we do.

03:35:12.768 --> 03:35:17.890
We now know that the family is almost dissolved.

03:35:17.890 --> 03:35:19.514
It was dismantled in the West.

03:35:19.514 --> 03:35:22.773
And it's coming to us in every state.

03:35:22.773 --> 03:35:28.899
In Saudi Arabia, Palestine, and Indonesia.

03:35:28.899 --> 03:35:31.737
It's dismantling

03:35:31.737 --> 03:35:34.981
Men refuse to marry more than woman.

03:35:34.981 --> 03:35:40.031
They expect a lot of troubles and big problems.

03:35:40.031 --> 03:35:42.402
He wants to be exempt me from it.

03:35:42.402 --> 03:35:45.003
Women almost don't want it.

03:35:45.003 --> 03:35:47.108
Both of them don't want kids.

03:35:47.108 --> 03:35:51.473
The institution of marriage is completely dissolving.

03:35:51.473 --> 03:35:53.563
But we ask why?

03:35:53.563 --> 03:35:58.094
We should ask why?

03:35:58.094 --> 03:36:02.271
Now let's go to the beginning in 1804

03:36:02.271 --> 03:36:05.189
In 1804

03:36:05.189 --> 03:36:09.928
The honorable professor Napoleon Bonaparte.

03:36:09.928 --> 03:36:16.777
He made a law and called it Napoleonic Code.

03:36:16.777 --> 03:36:22.595
Codified Napoleonic law.

03:36:22.595 --> 03:36:25.509
It changed the world.

03:36:25.509 --> 03:36:31.458
Because it was the first law codified in this way

03:36:31.458 --> 03:36:36.380
It brings all the authorities and power of the state.

03:36:36.380 --> 03:36:40.152
A section of this law

03:36:40.152 --> 03:36:43.808
under many other laws

03:36:43.808 --> 03:36:46.148
was for family.

03:36:46.148 --> 03:36:56.177
The state started enacting laws to redesign the family.

03:36:56.177 --> 03:36:59.409
When we say there is a legislation

03:36:59.409 --> 03:37:04.988
of course on the first level and that it's almost naïve

03:37:04.988 --> 03:37:12.026
The state legislated a law that is applied to all as a system.

03:37:12.026 --> 03:37:15.655
This is a correct concept, but naïve.

03:37:15.655 --> 03:37:18.807
The not naïve explanation

03:37:18.807 --> 03:37:20.661
is to ask the question of

03:37:20.661 --> 03:37:24.377
what is this law going to do to society?

03:37:24.377 --> 03:37:29.133
If you see it from 1804 until this day

03:37:29.133 --> 03:37:34.749
The laws of all states are laws to corrupt the family

03:37:34.749 --> 03:37:37.461
this is not their goal

03:37:37.461 --> 03:37:41.257
but its effects and consequences were the corruption of the family.

03:37:41.257 --> 03:37:48.905
The dissolution of the family today is completely linked to the laws and the capitalist system.

03:37:48.905 --> 03:37:51.475
Nothing else can explain them.

03:37:51.475 --> 03:37:56.513
Capitalist and the state laws

03:37:56.513 --> 03:38:01.405
This shows you that capitalism and the state work together.

03:38:01.405 --> 03:38:06.083
The family broke up

03:38:06.083 --> 03:38:10.817
because it's a small section of the big picture

03:38:10.817 --> 03:38:15.299
which the state

03:38:15.299 --> 03:38:21.521
decompose society and divide it into sections

03:38:21.521 --> 03:38:24.108
The goal of the state is 

03:38:24.108 --> 03:38:28.019
always to eliminate large groups

03:38:28.019 --> 03:38:30.759
which has its own internal rules and ethics.

03:38:30.759 --> 03:38:33.917
Let me give you a simple example

03:38:33.917 --> 03:38:36.415
If you look at the Middle Eastern states

03:38:36.415 --> 03:38:40.975
not Saudi Arabia, but Egypt and Israel

03:38:40.975 --> 03:38:45.067
Of course Israel has a colonial plan

03:38:45.067 --> 03:38:47.976
But it has something to share with Egypt

03:38:47.976 --> 03:38:58.431
Both want their Bedouins population to be in one concentrated area

03:38:58.431 --> 03:39:01.891
and don't allow them to roam with their tents

03:39:01.891 --> 03:39:07.023
but to give them homes to settle in it and with schools and whatnot.

03:39:07.023 --> 03:39:10.667
Because Bedouins are tribes.

03:39:10.667 --> 03:39:17.241
And tribes have devotion and respect for its own laws only.

03:39:17.241 --> 03:39:21.737
They want to roam and keep their habits and customs and they are independent people.

03:39:21.737 --> 03:39:24.477
Bedouins are free people.

03:39:24.477 --> 03:39:29.348
The most free people on earth in the last century were the Bedouins of the world.

03:39:29.348 --> 03:39:35.597
They live their lives as they will, but they face state opposition wherever they are.

03:39:35.597 --> 03:39:39.574
The state wanted them settled, because it want to dismantle them.

03:39:39.574 --> 03:39:42.061
It teaches them in its schools.

03:39:42.061 --> 03:39:46.931
It gives them its laws of marriage.

03:39:46.931 --> 03:39:51.262
Then it dismantle them to become single individuals that can be controled

03:39:51.262 --> 03:39:54.030
by the state and capitalism.

03:39:54.030 --> 03:39:57.321
This is the goal of the state.

03:39:57.321 --> 03:40:01.309
Wait a second, I want to go back to what is said.

03:40:01.309 --> 03:40:06.375
You asked me how the modern state can't be Islamic state?

03:40:06.375 --> 03:40:12.162
You are thinking that as long as I can pray and fast, it means that I am a Muslim living in a modern state.

03:40:12.162 --> 03:40:16.744
No, but modern countries are dismantling society under your feet.

03:40:16.744 --> 03:40:23.762
Not you, but the generation of your children,

03:40:23.762 --> 03:40:26.884
is going to face the same problems

03:40:26.884 --> 03:40:29.432
there will be family, aunts, uncles, or love

03:40:29.432 --> 03:40:31.379
from the big family

03:40:31.379 --> 03:40:34.096
They will be alone and miserable in the world.

03:40:34.096 --> 03:40:35.943
This is the fate of all.

03:40:35.943 --> 03:40:42.090
Millions on millions proved this before us.

03:40:42.090 --> 03:40:49.615
Are the dismantle of the family and the loss of all your relatives

03:40:49.615 --> 03:40:52.406
and they became strangers to you, a part of Islam?

03:40:52.406 --> 03:40:57.440
Islam mainly depends on the group.

03:40:57.440 --> 03:41:00.843
There is no Islam without a group.

03:41:00.843 --> 03:41:04.295
There is no good without the group.

03:41:04.295 --> 03:41:09.086
The good deeds, cooperation, affection

03:41:09.086 --> 03:41:12.939
love, and friendship in Islam isn't there without the group.

03:41:12.939 --> 03:41:15.860
The state dismantles groups.

03:41:15.860 --> 03:41:21.540
Maybe it's a bit slower in our states

03:41:21.540 --> 03:41:24.106
but in the end this is where it's headed.

03:41:24.106 --> 03:41:28.065
Is this because the state or globalization?

03:41:28.065 --> 03:41:35.791
Globalization is one of the modernity sides

03:41:35.791 --> 03:41:41.484
and the state and capitalism.

03:41:41.484 --> 03:41:47.439
It's like the ball of football

03:41:47.439 --> 03:41:53.372
shapes of octagonal stitched together.

03:41:53.372 --> 03:42:00.000
Each one has its place by the others and has its own content

03:42:00.000 --> 03:42:01.487
visualize it like that.

03:42:01.487 --> 03:42:03.187
This is modernity.

03:42:03.187 --> 03:42:06.203
You have globalization

03:42:06.203 --> 03:42:11.775
The modern science, and this has its own story that we haven't touched today.

03:42:11.775 --> 03:42:14.816
Science and its holiness

03:42:14.816 --> 03:42:19.730
Companies, economy and banks

03:42:19.730 --> 03:42:22.406
capitalism, and the state.

03:42:22.406 --> 03:42:26.737
All of them together make this phenomenon.

03:42:26.737 --> 03:42:30.259
Globalization is not different.

03:42:30.259 --> 03:42:35.708
It's one side or a dynamic section of the sections we talked about.

03:42:35.708 --> 03:42:39.399
When I talk about the state and capitalism, I'm talking about globalization at the same time.

03:42:39.399 --> 03:42:42.152
Even though I didn't mention it.

03:42:42.152 --> 03:42:44.392
